{"id":132366,"type":2,"name":"Der Fuehrer's Face","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b9/ef/132366_GAXG8.jpg","rating":{"total":31,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":8,"7":13,"8":9,"9":0,"10":0},"score":7},"summary":"　　本动画片曾荣获1943年奥斯卡最佳动画片奖，并在2006年法国安锡（Annecy）国际动画电影节上被评为“动画的世纪•100部作品”第87名。 \r\n　　唐老鸭做了一个噩梦，梦中他成了纳粹统治下的一名奴隶。每天不但要起早贪黑地拼命干活，还要随时听命于各种口号、不停地对遍地都是的希特勒的照片敬礼，然而它的待遇，实在差到不能再差，干活时，动不动就会被监工拳打脚踢，吃的面包干到难以下咽。一天，它在流水线加工大大小小的子弹时，精神逐渐失常，最终爆发。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>元首的面孔</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>製作: </span><a href=\"/person/6816\">Walt Disney Pictures</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/13956\">Walt Disney Animation Studios</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1943-01-01</li><li><span>片长: </span>8 分钟</li><li><span>IMDb链接: </span>tt0035794</li><li><span>语言: </span>德语 / 英语</li><li><span>制片国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>类型: </span>喜剧 / 动画 / 短片 / 家庭 / 战争</li><li><span>主演: </span>比利·布莱彻 / 克拉伦斯·纳什</li><li><span>编剧: </span>克拉伦斯·纳什</li><li><span>导演: </span>Jack Kinney</li>","collection":{"wish":8,"collect":58,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":23},{"name":"欧美","count":12},{"name":"奥斯卡","count":9},{"name":"1943","count":7},{"name":"迪士尼","count":6},{"name":"讽刺","count":5},{"name":"Disney","count":4},{"name":"元首","count":3},{"name":"唐老鸭","count":3},{"name":"美国","count":2},{"name":"唱歌","count":2},{"name":"Oscars","count":1},{"name":"1940s","count":1},{"name":"JackKinney","count":1},{"name":"BillyBletcher","count":1},{"name":"短片&OVA","count":1},{"name":"ClarenceNash","count":1},{"name":"US","count":1},{"name":"剧场版","count":1},{"name":"美国动画","count":1},{"name":"中庸","count":1},{"name":"WaltDisney","count":1},{"name":"上古","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":897706,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/897706","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":6816,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4f/85/6816_prsn_MGpfY.jpg","name":"迪士尼电影公司","desc":"製作"},{"id":13956,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/